  <h1 class="gd-h1">Is Heliskiing Safe?</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">The honest answer: heliskiing carries <strong>real risk that cannot be eliminated</strong>, but with a quality operator it is a carefully managed activity, and the overwhelming majority of trips are incident-free. Below we set out the risks plainly and how they are controlled, so you can decide with clear eyes before browsing <a href="/packages">packages</a> or reading about <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
